  "text": "In the R software, differentially expressed genes (DEGs) between BLCA and normal tissues were identified using Wilcoxon test after within-array replicate probes were replaced with their average via limma package [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The p-value was adjusted with the false discovery rate (FDR) [CITATION_3] . FDR < 0.05 and |log2 (FC)| value > 1 was considered significant.",
